1
00:02:13,159 --> 00:02:14,120
Bring it on!

2
00:03:02,879 --> 00:03:04,199
My reinforcements have arrived!

3
00:03:05,639 --> 00:03:06,960
You're doomed!

4
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:22,400
Light the torch!

5
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:51,639
Kill!

6
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,120
Kill!

7
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,120
Kill!

8
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,719
Kill!

9
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:56,759
Kill!

10
00:03:56,919 --> 00:03:58,680
Kill!

11
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:01,639
Kill!

12
00:04:03,879 --> 00:04:05,280
Kill!

13
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:08,479
Kill!

14
00:04:08,719 --> 00:04:12,240
Kill!

15
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,600
The Great Yan reinforcements!

16
00:05:02,519 --> 00:05:03,720
Yanyun!

17
00:06:02,519 --> 00:06:03,639
[Slay them!]

18
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:06,319
[Charge!]

19
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:25,799
By Your Highness's side,

20
00:09:25,799 --> 00:09:26,919
there may be loyal and upright men,

21
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:29,600
and there may also be treacherous sycophants.

22
00:09:31,399 --> 00:09:32,759
But the ones like Lord Ye

23
00:09:33,679 --> 00:09:35,279
must never be near you.

24
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:38,799
What kind of man am I?

25
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:40,440
You're a man

26
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:43,200
consumed by despair.

27
00:14:30,279 --> 00:14:30,960
Sir.

28
00:15:01,519 --> 00:15:03,039
You shouldn't call me Lord.

29
00:15:04,039 --> 00:15:05,279
Jinxian is your cousin,

30
00:15:05,960 --> 00:15:07,080
yet my own nephew.

31
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:08,879
You should call me uncle

32
00:15:10,279 --> 00:15:11,360
like he does.

33
00:15:14,120 --> 00:15:15,360
It's not so easy

34
00:15:16,039 --> 00:15:17,159
to take advantage of me.

35
00:15:20,360 --> 00:15:21,200
If you ask me,

36
00:15:22,480 --> 00:15:23,720
that face is all you've got.

37
00:15:24,279 --> 00:15:25,399
Or with your nature,

38
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:27,000
who would like to marry you?

39
00:15:28,399 --> 00:15:29,240
What happened?

40
00:15:30,600 --> 00:15:31,240
What are you doing?

41
00:15:32,399 --> 00:15:33,240
Grab me like this?

42
00:15:34,279 --> 00:15:35,159
May lightning strike me dead

43
00:15:35,399 --> 00:15:36,240
if I tell a lie.

44
00:15:37,039 --> 00:15:37,840
And may lightning strike you dead

45
00:15:38,159 --> 00:15:39,080
if you lie.

46
00:15:40,039 --> 00:15:41,000
Meeting you

47
00:15:41,200 --> 00:15:42,879
is already my doom.

48
00:15:43,240 --> 00:15:45,200
Gu Jinzhao, how dare you!

49
00:15:52,759 --> 00:15:53,879
Do you truly not understand,

50
00:15:54,440 --> 00:15:55,440
or pretend not to?

51
00:15:56,360 --> 00:15:57,120
I do all this

52
00:15:57,679 --> 00:15:58,679
for your sake.

53
00:16:04,519 --> 00:16:05,759
[Your mother was murdered.]

54
00:16:06,919 --> 00:16:07,600
[Who did this?]

55
00:16:08,159 --> 00:16:09,039
I will kill them for you.

56
00:16:10,919 --> 00:16:12,000
[You have so many carriages,]

57
00:16:12,360 --> 00:16:13,360
[yet only a handful of guards.]

58
00:16:14,120 --> 00:16:15,679
You're clearly sitting ducks.

59
00:16:17,120 --> 00:16:18,120
With them guarding you,

60
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:20,000
I can rest easier.

61
00:16:23,559 --> 00:16:24,279
This is...

62
00:16:24,960 --> 00:16:25,720
A bracelet.

63
00:16:27,519 --> 00:16:28,360
It came from a raid,

64
00:16:29,200 --> 00:16:30,080
but it's now legally cleared.

65
00:16:30,679 --> 00:16:31,440
Don't worry.

66
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:33,759
If you think it's filthy,

67
00:16:34,360 --> 00:16:35,039
just toss it.

68
00:16:40,240 --> 00:16:41,399
Gu Jinzhao!

69
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:53,840
What a coincidence!

70
00:16:54,639 --> 00:16:55,600
Fancy meeting you here.

71
00:18:17,720 --> 00:18:18,240
Sir!

72
00:18:37,279 --> 00:18:37,960
How is Yanyun?

73
00:18:40,240 --> 00:18:40,880
Rest assured.

74
00:18:41,880 --> 00:18:42,519
He just woke up.

75
00:18:43,240 --> 00:18:43,759
He is fine.

76
00:18:54,000 --> 00:18:54,880
Keep him company for a while

77
00:19:48,119 --> 00:19:48,759
[Gu Jinzhao,]

78
00:19:49,480 --> 00:19:50,640
[if you are reading this letter,]

79
00:19:51,519 --> 00:19:52,680
[there is only one possibility that]

80
00:19:53,920 --> 00:19:55,160
[I am done for.]

81
00:19:58,440 --> 00:19:59,599
[Do not feel guilty.]

82
00:20:00,680 --> 00:20:01,759
[I march to the borderlands this time]

83
00:20:02,200 --> 00:20:02,960
[not only for you,]

84
00:20:03,720 --> 00:20:04,839
[but also for myself.]

85
00:20:06,920 --> 00:20:08,000
[Doc told me that]

86
00:20:09,039 --> 00:20:10,079
[my heart ailment is severe,]

87
00:20:10,640 --> 00:20:11,400
[and I have less than three years to live.]

88
00:20:12,720 --> 00:20:13,960
[Rather than fading away in lethargy,]

89
00:20:15,160 --> 00:20:16,440
[I choose to die boldly and fiercely.]

90
00:20:17,720 --> 00:20:18,400
[In the past,]

91
00:20:18,920 --> 00:20:20,519
[My dad is always yelling at me that I can't learn martial arts,]

92
00:20:21,680 --> 00:20:22,359
[can't command an army,]

93
00:20:22,599 --> 00:20:24,440
[and can't even hold up the reputation of Marquis's.]

94
00:20:25,759 --> 00:20:26,640
[But this time,]

95
00:20:27,400 --> 00:20:28,200
[I've commanded an army,]

96
00:20:28,960 --> 00:20:29,599
[fought battles,]

97
00:20:30,680 --> 00:20:31,920
[and shall die]

98
00:20:32,640 --> 00:20:33,559
[on the battlefield.]

99
00:20:34,519 --> 00:20:35,519
[When we meet in the netherworld,]

100
00:20:36,160 --> 00:20:37,319
[I will stand tall and proud,]

101
00:20:38,319 --> 00:20:39,200
[and tell him face‑to‑face that]

102
00:20:39,720 --> 00:20:40,359
[I, Ye Xian,]

103
00:20:40,880 --> 00:20:41,920
[have brought no shame to Ye.]

104
00:20:44,880 --> 00:20:45,720
[Are you crying?]

105
00:20:46,480 --> 00:20:47,440
[Do not cry.]

106
00:20:47,880 --> 00:20:49,119
[You ought to be happy for me.]

107
00:20:50,119 --> 00:20:51,160
[It's not that]

108
00:20:52,279 --> 00:20:53,119
[I have no regrets.]

109
00:20:54,160 --> 00:20:55,400
[My mother still lives,]

110
00:20:56,440 --> 00:20:57,640
[but I can't repay her filial piety.]

111
00:20:58,880 --> 00:20:59,880
[Please look after her]

112
00:21:01,839 --> 00:21:02,519
[and my sister for me.]

113
00:21:03,240 --> 00:21:04,640
[My brother‑in‑law is good‑for‑nothing.]

114
00:21:05,839 --> 00:21:06,799
[But my sister is proud,]

115
00:21:08,640 --> 00:21:09,240
[and keeps her sorrows]

116
00:21:09,240 --> 00:21:10,359
[bottled up inside.]

117
00:21:11,039 --> 00:21:11,920
[She likes you.]

118
00:21:12,519 --> 00:21:14,039
[So please visit her often.]

119
00:21:16,440 --> 00:21:18,680
[Then, Xue Qinglan.]

120
00:21:19,440 --> 00:21:20,680
[Such a good girl,]

121
00:21:21,519 --> 00:21:22,400
[yet she fell for me.]

122
00:21:23,039 --> 00:21:24,279
[How foolish of her!]

123
00:21:26,480 --> 00:21:27,519
[When she marries,]

124
00:21:27,960 --> 00:21:29,160
[send her a wedding gift on my behalf.]

125
00:21:30,400 --> 00:21:30,839
[Oh, and]

126
00:21:31,799 --> 00:21:32,440
[Baopu the cat.]

127
00:21:33,079 --> 00:21:34,400
[Such a lovely cat,]

128
00:21:35,920 --> 00:21:37,000
[whom I never once praised.]

129
00:21:39,599 --> 00:21:40,240
[Please praise it for me]
[in the future.]

130
00:21:42,599 --> 00:21:43,799
[As for Chen Yanyun,]

131
00:21:45,960 --> 00:21:46,799
[that scoundrel,]

132
00:21:47,240 --> 00:21:48,119
[who always outshines me,]

133
00:21:50,160 --> 00:21:51,680
[even secretly stole your heart from me.]

134
00:21:52,400 --> 00:21:53,279
[I shall never forgive him.]

135
00:21:55,319 --> 00:21:56,440
[They say good men die young,]

136
00:21:56,519 --> 00:21:57,480
[while villains live long.]

137
00:21:59,559 --> 00:22:00,319
[With all his]

138
00:22:00,319 --> 00:22:01,680
[schemes and tricks,]

139
00:22:02,799 --> 00:22:04,319
[he will probably live to grow old with you.]

140
00:22:05,279 --> 00:22:06,160
[If so,]

141
00:22:07,000 --> 00:22:08,119
[that is the only decent thing he has ever done.]

142
00:22:08,359 --> 00:22:08,960
[Still,]

143
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:10,279
[now that I die in battle,]

144
00:22:11,240 --> 00:22:12,000
[you will never forget me]

145
00:22:12,000 --> 00:22:13,039
[for the rest of your life.]

146
00:22:14,240 --> 00:22:15,240
[To live in your heart]
[in this way,]

147
00:22:17,160 --> 00:22:18,400
[that's one win over him.]

148
00:22:20,720 --> 00:22:21,880
[Just thinking of it makes me glad.]

149
00:22:23,240 --> 00:22:23,599
[Make sure]

150
00:22:23,599 --> 00:22:24,640
[you tell him this part]

151
00:22:25,079 --> 00:22:25,880
[Keep that in mind.]

152
00:22:29,799 --> 00:22:30,240
[Oh,]
[one more thing.]

153
00:22:31,759 --> 00:22:32,720
[If I die,]

154
00:22:33,039 --> 00:22:34,000
[keep the name of the Ye Army]

155
00:22:35,000 --> 00:22:36,000
[if they wanna keep using it.]

156
00:22:37,559 --> 00:22:39,119
[It is a pity to waste such military merit,]

157
00:22:40,279 --> 00:22:40,839
[but it doesn't matter.]

158
00:22:41,720 --> 00:22:42,680
[Consider it my gift to him.]

159
00:22:44,000 --> 00:22:44,519
[Well.]

160
00:22:45,279 --> 00:22:46,400
[That's all.]

161
00:22:48,200 --> 00:22:48,920
[I shall take my leave first.]

162
00:22:50,440 --> 00:22:51,640
[To have met you in my life]

163
00:22:53,000 --> 00:22:54,480
[is the greatest fortune of mine.]

164
00:22:57,400 --> 00:22:57,839
[Farewell.]

165
00:22:58,799 --> 00:22:59,359
[Farewell.]

166
00:23:47,799 --> 00:23:48,720
I led

167
00:23:48,880 --> 00:23:50,359
two thousand light cavalrymen,

168
00:23:50,759 --> 00:23:51,920
marching day and night,

169
00:23:52,720 --> 00:23:53,960
yet still arrived too late.

170
00:23:54,519 --> 00:23:55,079
Otherwise,

171
00:23:56,000 --> 00:23:57,119
Lord Ye would not have perished.

172
00:24:01,640 --> 00:24:02,480
This time, I swear to

173
00:24:03,000 --> 00:24:05,119
escort you safely back to the capital.

174
00:24:16,799 --> 00:24:17,640
I am not

175
00:24:18,240 --> 00:24:19,200
planning to return yet.

176
00:24:20,680 --> 00:24:21,599
Before I came here,

177
00:24:21,960 --> 00:24:23,359
the Governor‑General repeatedly ordered me

178
00:24:23,799 --> 00:24:24,720
to escort you safely back

179
00:24:24,880 --> 00:24:26,680
to the capital in person.

180
00:24:27,599 --> 00:24:28,319
Are you afraid that

181
00:24:28,640 --> 00:24:29,480
after your return,

182
00:24:30,079 --> 00:24:31,240
Fu Hailian will harm you?

183
00:24:33,599 --> 00:24:35,400
I fear not for myself.

184
00:24:37,079 --> 00:24:37,640
Right now,

185
00:24:38,480 --> 00:24:40,160
Shi City and Men Plateau have fallen.

186
00:24:40,720 --> 00:24:42,559
Though Yi County is guarded by ten thousand elite soldiers,

187
00:24:43,519 --> 00:24:44,359
the Northern Barbarians

188
00:24:44,519 --> 00:24:46,000
keep amassing their troops.

189
00:24:46,599 --> 00:24:47,119
The imperial court must

190
00:24:48,119 --> 00:24:48,880
immediately dispatch

191
00:24:48,880 --> 00:24:50,599
elite troops from the Capital Garrison

192
00:24:50,799 --> 00:24:51,720
to Yi County to resist the enemy.

193
00:24:53,119 --> 00:24:54,680
Yet all military deployments

194
00:24:55,599 --> 00:24:56,559
require mediation

195
00:24:56,920 --> 00:24:57,799
from the Grand Council,

196
00:24:59,200 --> 00:25:00,480
and demand united efforts from officials

197
00:25:00,599 --> 00:25:02,880
both in and out of court to be carried out.

198
00:25:03,880 --> 00:25:05,079
If I return to the capital now,

199
00:25:07,480 --> 00:25:08,880
the truth that Fu colluded

200
00:25:10,440 --> 00:25:11,839
with the Chunyuan Sect

201
00:25:11,839 --> 00:25:12,759
will surely be exposed.

202
00:25:14,000 --> 00:25:14,799
By then,

203
00:25:17,160 --> 00:25:19,119
the court will plunge into chaos.

204
00:25:21,039 --> 00:25:22,359
Not to mention resisting the enemy,

205
00:25:22,519 --> 00:25:23,200
even

206
00:25:23,559 --> 00:25:24,559
dispatching troops

207
00:25:25,640 --> 00:25:26,599
may be impossible

208
00:25:27,200 --> 00:25:28,279
due to the

209
00:25:28,920 --> 00:25:29,960
court turmoil.

210
00:25:32,319 --> 00:25:32,799
Go report this way

211
00:25:32,799 --> 00:25:33,960
to Yanzhang.

212
00:25:34,400 --> 00:25:35,400
He will not blame you.

213
00:25:36,720 --> 00:25:38,119
I've said it before, you civil officials...

214
00:25:38,359 --> 00:25:39,359
What should we do?

215
00:25:43,920 --> 00:25:44,920
Unless

216
00:25:47,039 --> 00:25:48,319
I truly die here.

217
00:26:39,079 --> 00:26:39,599
Mom!

218
00:26:39,759 --> 00:26:40,920
Mom insisted on coming here,

219
00:26:40,920 --> 00:26:41,799
and I could not stop her.

220
00:27:18,279 --> 00:27:18,920
Mom...

221
00:27:21,079 --> 00:27:22,559
this place is unsafe to linger.

222
00:27:23,279 --> 00:27:23,920
Let us

223
00:27:23,920 --> 00:27:25,319
return to the Manor first.

224
00:27:28,880 --> 00:27:29,440
Let's go.
Mom...

225
00:28:40,880 --> 00:28:42,119
Yanyun,

226
00:28:44,000 --> 00:28:45,559
you sacrificed for the Great Yan.

227
00:28:46,240 --> 00:28:47,319
Upon hearing this,

228
00:28:47,799 --> 00:28:49,359
I'm overwhelmed with grief.

229
00:28:54,279 --> 00:28:55,359
Mrs. Chen, please

230
00:28:56,359 --> 00:28:57,920
send Yanyun's coffin

231
00:28:58,839 --> 00:29:01,000
to Xuanmiao Temple

232
00:29:01,640 --> 00:29:03,200
for all officials to pay their respects.

233
00:29:06,559 --> 00:29:07,839
What if I refuse?

234
00:29:20,319 --> 00:29:21,480
That can't be allowed.

235
00:29:26,400 --> 00:29:27,319
I refuse.

236
00:29:28,799 --> 00:29:29,640
Insolence!

237
00:29:30,720 --> 00:29:31,640
I don't believe

238
00:29:32,839 --> 00:29:34,640
you dare to incur universal condemnation

239
00:29:35,519 --> 00:29:36,839
and force the widow of a loyal minister

240
00:29:37,119 --> 00:29:38,319
to death so boldly!

241
00:30:03,759 --> 00:30:06,200
Nor do I believe you wish to die.

242
00:30:10,279 --> 00:30:11,920
I advise you not to provoke me.

243
00:30:12,680 --> 00:30:14,279
Yanyun died a heroic death

244
00:30:15,160 --> 00:30:16,200
on the battlefield.

245
00:30:16,880 --> 00:30:18,279
As his wife,

246
00:30:19,759 --> 00:30:21,240
I fear no death.

247
00:30:58,880 --> 00:30:59,640
Okay.

248
00:31:17,440 --> 00:31:18,440
Go back to the Manor!

249
00:32:14,240 --> 00:32:14,920
Sir,

250
00:32:15,720 --> 00:32:16,640
by now, the lady

251
00:32:17,079 --> 00:32:18,279
should have reached the capital.

252
00:32:21,200 --> 00:32:22,440
Judging by the days,

253
00:32:23,720 --> 00:32:24,839
she ought to have arrived.

254
00:32:30,279 --> 00:32:31,480
I wonder if she

255
00:32:32,680 --> 00:32:34,119
can secure reinforcement troops.

256
00:32:34,559 --> 00:32:35,400
I...

257
00:32:36,200 --> 00:32:37,240
I am rather worried.

258
00:32:43,759 --> 00:32:45,279
She will make it happen.

259
00:32:46,160 --> 00:32:47,680
I believe in her.

260
00:33:25,000 --> 00:33:26,200
I see you zoning out.

261
00:33:26,880 --> 00:33:27,799
Are you tired?

262
00:33:28,960 --> 00:33:30,000
Let me massage you.

263
00:33:31,640 --> 00:33:32,359
I used to do this

264
00:33:33,200 --> 00:33:34,640
for my grandma.

265
00:33:35,880 --> 00:33:36,720
I was thinking

266
00:33:38,200 --> 00:33:39,319
if there is a way

267
00:33:41,400 --> 00:33:41,960
to keep you from

268
00:33:41,960 --> 00:33:43,240
taking such great risks.

269
00:33:44,279 --> 00:33:45,279
What risk am I in?

270
00:33:46,519 --> 00:33:47,640
I'm just going back to the capital.

271
00:33:49,519 --> 00:33:51,200
Do you really fear

272
00:33:51,200 --> 00:33:53,160
Fu Hailian will bite me?

273
00:33:55,880 --> 00:33:56,839
I just worry about you.

274
00:34:01,480 --> 00:34:02,720
You need not worry about me.

275
00:34:04,480 --> 00:34:05,279
Yi County has tall city walls,
easy to defend yet hard to attack.

276
00:34:06,559 --> 00:34:07,279
Six months ago,

277
00:34:07,559 --> 00:34:08,840
the walls were reinforced again.

278
00:34:09,199 --> 00:34:10,960
The Northern Barbarians know nothing about siege warfare.

279
00:34:12,360 --> 00:34:13,159
In the short term,

280
00:34:14,559 --> 00:34:15,880
they can do nothing to us.

281
00:34:19,599 --> 00:34:20,760
So according to you,

282
00:34:21,039 --> 00:34:23,079
we are both safe.

283
00:34:32,440 --> 00:34:33,000
It's for you.

284
00:34:36,960 --> 00:34:37,559
What's this?

285
00:34:38,639 --> 00:34:39,599
This is brought by Qingpu

286
00:34:39,599 --> 00:34:40,960
from Pingyang Prefecture.

287
00:34:42,360 --> 00:34:43,559
I won't need them

288
00:34:43,559 --> 00:34:44,440
after I return to the capital.

289
00:34:45,639 --> 00:34:46,760
If you miss me,

290
00:34:46,880 --> 00:34:47,760
have one.

291
00:34:57,719 --> 00:34:58,519
How many are there?

292
00:34:59,239 --> 00:34:59,800
Guess.

293
00:35:01,400 --> 00:35:02,400
From the feel of it,

294
00:35:04,960 --> 00:35:05,800
I could finish all of them
in two hours.

295
00:35:10,800 --> 00:35:11,480
Don't you have anything

296
00:35:11,480 --> 00:35:12,599
to give me?

297
00:35:14,599 --> 00:35:15,719
Behind the painting in the study,

298
00:35:16,960 --> 00:35:18,000
there's a box.

299
00:35:18,920 --> 00:35:19,519
Inside it are

300
00:35:19,519 --> 00:35:21,199
my most precious belongings.

301
00:35:23,679 --> 00:35:24,440
If I...

302
00:35:28,800 --> 00:35:30,559
Just keep them as a memento.

303
00:35:32,679 --> 00:35:33,639
Don't talk nonsense.

304
00:35:34,280 --> 00:35:35,119
What memento?

305
00:35:36,039 --> 00:35:36,800
I only want you.

306
00:35:38,119 --> 00:35:38,760
Clear?

307
00:35:45,119 --> 00:35:45,800
Clear.

308
00:35:49,039 --> 00:35:49,960
Wait for me.

309
00:35:51,960 --> 00:35:53,119
I will find a way

310
00:35:53,679 --> 00:35:54,800
to persuade the court to send troops.

311
00:35:56,400 --> 00:35:57,639
Sending troops matters,

312
00:35:59,440 --> 00:36:00,480
but to me,

313
00:36:04,599 --> 00:36:06,159
your safety matters far more.

314
00:36:09,239 --> 00:36:10,599
In my whole life,

315
00:36:11,960 --> 00:36:13,159
I have put the court, the nation,

316
00:36:14,280 --> 00:36:15,400
the realm and the world

317
00:36:15,400 --> 00:36:17,119
above everything else in my heart.

318
00:36:19,679 --> 00:36:20,800
But this time...

319
00:36:27,440 --> 00:36:28,079
I want you.

320
00:36:29,719 --> 00:36:30,400
Don't risk your life

321
00:36:30,400 --> 00:36:31,719
for any cause.

322
00:36:33,960 --> 00:36:35,119
I want you to live,

323
00:36:35,599 --> 00:36:36,119
okay?

324
00:37:11,320 --> 00:37:12,039
Miss Gu.

325
00:37:12,599 --> 00:37:13,159
Jinzhao.

326
00:37:14,039 --> 00:37:14,639
My condolences.

327
00:37:17,400 --> 00:37:18,840
Are the ones of Daxin Ancestral Clan here?

328
00:37:19,440 --> 00:37:20,239
Not yet.

329
00:37:21,000 --> 00:37:21,840
Hurry back to Daxin Manor,

330
00:37:22,199 --> 00:37:23,079
and invite Grandma and the others

331
00:37:23,239 --> 00:37:23,960
to pay their respects.

332
00:37:24,159 --> 00:37:25,760
Make sure Auntie comes as well.

333
00:37:27,079 --> 00:37:27,519
Okay.
Go now.

334
00:37:29,760 --> 00:37:30,199
Let's go.

335
00:37:37,559 --> 00:37:38,159
Mom,

336
00:37:39,760 --> 00:37:40,280
sister-in-law,

337
00:37:41,320 --> 00:37:42,639
I have something to tell you.

338
00:37:47,719 --> 00:37:48,360
Mom,

339
00:37:48,639 --> 00:37:49,480
in fact,

340
00:37:50,840 --> 00:37:51,960
Yanyun is still alive.

341
00:37:55,039 --> 00:37:56,440
What?

342
00:37:56,920 --> 00:37:57,800
It's true.

343
00:37:58,039 --> 00:37:58,639
Mom,

344
00:37:59,360 --> 00:38:00,280
it is all my fault.

345
00:38:00,840 --> 00:38:01,639
I did not

346
00:38:02,000 --> 00:38:03,000
tell you beforehand,

347
00:38:03,639 --> 00:38:05,039
causing you such grief.

348
00:38:05,960 --> 00:38:07,039
It is my mistake.

349
00:38:07,519 --> 00:38:08,599
Please forgive me.

350
00:38:10,559 --> 00:38:11,599
I once thought

351
00:38:12,639 --> 00:38:13,480
it was merely

352
00:38:13,480 --> 00:38:14,719
my wishful thinking.

353
00:38:19,000 --> 00:38:19,519
Mom.

354
00:38:19,519 --> 00:38:20,960
Mom.

355
00:38:21,079 --> 00:38:21,679
Mom.

356
00:38:24,000 --> 00:38:24,559
Mom.
Yanyun is alive.

357
00:38:25,559 --> 00:38:26,960
You should be happy!

358
00:38:27,519 --> 00:38:28,039
Mom.

359
00:38:29,920 --> 00:38:32,239
Yes, I am.

360
00:38:33,719 --> 00:38:36,280
Yet I hate myself.

361
00:38:39,239 --> 00:38:40,320
Since I

362
00:38:41,400 --> 00:38:43,800
thought he was gone,

363
00:38:45,480 --> 00:38:46,840
every night,

364
00:38:48,000 --> 00:38:49,599
the moment I close my eyes,

365
00:38:50,760 --> 00:38:53,800
I can see him as a little boy.

366
00:38:55,480 --> 00:38:57,119
He was mature from childhood.

367
00:38:58,880 --> 00:39:00,400
Among all my children,

368
00:39:01,440 --> 00:39:03,239
he was the most sensible.

369
00:39:03,719 --> 00:39:06,360
But that's why

370
00:39:06,679 --> 00:39:07,639
whenever

371
00:39:08,760 --> 00:39:10,760
his brothers quarreled,

372
00:39:11,599 --> 00:39:12,920
I never judged who was right

373
00:39:13,679 --> 00:39:15,679
and I always scolded him first.

374
00:39:19,199 --> 00:39:20,440
But I forgot that

375
00:39:21,800 --> 00:39:23,519
he was just a child too.

376
00:39:25,159 --> 00:39:25,960
Later,

377
00:39:26,400 --> 00:39:27,480
he grew up,

378
00:39:28,119 --> 00:39:29,559
becoming the most accomplished

379
00:39:29,559 --> 00:39:31,480
among his brothers.

380
00:39:32,880 --> 00:39:34,159
Yet I felt he

381
00:39:34,679 --> 00:39:35,960
grew distant from me,

382
00:39:37,199 --> 00:39:38,840
telling me nothing.

383
00:39:40,159 --> 00:39:41,280
And I kept

384
00:39:41,920 --> 00:39:43,000
burdening him with everything.

385
00:39:43,960 --> 00:39:45,079
I made him plan

386
00:39:46,360 --> 00:39:48,519
for Yanzhang's future,

387
00:39:49,880 --> 00:39:50,440
and

388
00:39:51,480 --> 00:39:52,639
clean up

389
00:39:53,199 --> 00:39:54,840
Yanwen's mess.

390
00:39:56,880 --> 00:39:58,360
To the outside world,

391
00:39:59,519 --> 00:40:00,639
he was my

392
00:40:00,920 --> 00:40:03,440
proudest son.

393
00:40:05,159 --> 00:40:06,280
But at home,

394
00:40:07,679 --> 00:40:08,800
I never once

395
00:40:09,920 --> 00:40:13,159
praised him from my heart.

396
00:40:18,199 --> 00:40:20,159
I was wrong.

397
00:40:21,599 --> 00:40:24,480
Terribly wrong.

398
00:40:26,000 --> 00:40:27,119
All these years,

399
00:40:28,159 --> 00:40:29,920
I wronged him endlessly.

400
00:40:31,679 --> 00:40:33,039
If I could start over,

401
00:40:33,639 --> 00:40:35,400
I would never do this again.

402
00:40:36,159 --> 00:40:37,119
I would...

403
00:40:37,440 --> 00:40:39,840
I would treat him well.

404
00:40:40,760 --> 00:40:41,519
I know.

405
00:40:42,400 --> 00:40:43,480
I know, mom.

406
00:40:44,960 --> 00:40:46,599
He's still alive.

407
00:40:47,519 --> 00:40:48,519
When he's back,

408
00:40:49,280 --> 00:40:50,440
you can tell him all this.

409
00:40:50,599 --> 00:40:51,360
Okay.

410
00:40:52,159 --> 00:40:52,880
Okay.

411
00:40:53,039 --> 00:40:54,039
Help mom up.

412
00:40:54,719 --> 00:40:55,440
Come mom.

413
00:41:04,079 --> 00:41:04,960
Thank you.

414
00:41:04,960 --> 00:41:06,320
My good girl.

415
00:41:07,480 --> 00:41:08,760
It is my duty.

416
00:41:09,199 --> 00:41:09,719
Sister-in-law...

417
00:41:10,920 --> 00:41:11,440
Then...

418
00:41:11,800 --> 00:41:12,719
who lies

419
00:41:12,880 --> 00:41:13,960
inside the coffin?

420
00:41:14,960 --> 00:41:15,519
Miss Gu.

421
00:41:20,559 --> 00:41:21,400
Grandma and Auntie

422
00:41:21,599 --> 00:41:22,639
have arrived.

423
00:41:24,000 --> 00:41:24,559
Sister-in-law,

424
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:25,760
please do me a favor.

425
00:41:26,159 --> 00:41:27,079
Look after mom

426
00:41:27,800 --> 00:41:28,800
and my grandma.

427
00:41:29,880 --> 00:41:30,360
Okay.

428
00:41:33,039 --> 00:41:33,719
Tell Auntie to
come to the study.

429
00:41:35,000 --> 00:41:35,440
Okay.

430
00:41:58,880 --> 00:41:59,519
Jinzhao,

431
00:42:00,000 --> 00:42:01,199
what happened?

432
00:42:01,800 --> 00:42:02,480
You asked Lan

433
00:42:02,480 --> 00:42:03,679
to invite me here for the condolence.

434
00:42:04,119 --> 00:42:05,039
Has something happened

435
00:42:05,199 --> 00:42:06,280
to Ye Xian?

436
00:42:08,880 --> 00:42:09,719
Auntie...

437
00:42:14,719 --> 00:42:15,480
Ye Xian...

438
00:42:18,519 --> 00:42:19,679
What happened to him?

439
00:42:21,880 --> 00:42:23,159
At Huxiao Gorge,

440
00:42:27,480 --> 00:42:28,679
he encountered the Northern Barbarians.

441
00:42:30,159 --> 00:42:30,880
He...

442
00:42:35,079 --> 00:42:36,079
He died.

443
00:42:51,840 --> 00:42:53,000
Before his death,

444
00:42:55,400 --> 00:42:56,679
he said not to tell others.

445
00:42:59,639 --> 00:43:01,360
He wanna keep using the banner of the Ye Army

446
00:43:03,360 --> 00:43:04,920
to resist the Northern Barbarians.

447
00:43:08,639 --> 00:43:09,400
That's why

448
00:43:14,679 --> 00:43:16,679
I could only bring him back in secret.

449
00:43:18,880 --> 00:43:19,559
Where is he?

450
00:43:20,280 --> 00:43:21,199
Where is he?
